        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant should be a resident of Bihar.\n   1. The applicant should be a farmer.\n   1. The applicant must have agricultural land a minimum of 0.25 acres (0.1 ha) and a maximum of 10 acres (4 ha).\n   1. The applicant must be registered on the DBT portal Agriculture Department.\n\n&gt; **Note 1:** The benefits of this scheme can be taken by ryot farmers on the basis of land documents and non-ryot farmers on the basis of contract form.\n\n&amp;gt; **Note 2:** Beneficiaries will be selected on first come first serve basis.\n\n&lt;br&gt;\n\n",
